name: Dean_(Kubaz)
content:
Dean was a male Kubaz technician of the Galactic Republic living during the Galactic War. Around 3641 BBY he was on Belsavis, where during the Invasion of Belsavis he and another Republic technician were captured by an escaped criminal Skadge and forced at gunpoint to retrieve information from the databanks of a destroyed astromech droid M3-OB.
Dean appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during a Bounty Hunter class mission on the planet Belsavis.
